Package: xcarver
Architecture: any
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), gcc, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: python3-pyewf
Description: Dual-engine forensic file carver
 xCarver recovers deleted files using two complementary engines:
 filesystem-aware recovery (preserving original names, paths, and
 timestamps) and raw carving with 119 byte-signature patterns.
 .
 Supports FAT12/16/32, exFAT, NTFS, ext2/3/4, HFS+, APFS, F2FS,
 Btrfs, and YAFFS2. High-performance C scanner using Aho-Corasick
 multi-pattern automaton with multithreaded processing.
 .
 Features: entropy-based skip for encrypted zones, CTF mode with
 entropy heatmap, session resumption, SHA256 cross-deduplication,
 recursive archive extraction, and external JSON signatures.
